START

Input Graph, Start Node, Goal Node and Heuristic Values

Create a Priority Queue

Insert Start Node with
f(n) = g(n) + h(n)

WHILE Priority Queue is not empty DO

    Remove node with smallest f(n)

    IF node is Goal THEN
        Print Optimal Cost
        STOP
    END IF

    IF node is not visited THEN
        Mark node as visited

        FOR each adjacent node DO

            g(n) = Current Cost + Edge Cost
            f(n) = g(n) + Heuristic

            Insert adjacent node with f(n)

        END FOR
    END IF

END WHILE

STOP
